title: Boring, Boring Chelsea 2.0
text: ✕ Boring, Boring Chelsea 2.0 Upgraded by Antonio Conte, London is Blue talks about how this team is different than the 2014/15 title champions. Photo by Michael Regan/Getty Images London is Blue are... Special Guest, Jeff Borzello, @jeffborzello Listen In Episode Summary West Ham dispatched in a 2-0 – oh, wait, they scored in the last minute of stoppage time? Fine . – 2-1 affair, Chelseas continue their quest to return to the Champions League, win the Premier League title, and maybe even do a double by stomping over Manchester United in the FA Cup. We break down the match, and look ahead to next week, with the help of ESPN’s Jeff Borzello. Housekeeping Leave us an iTunes review ! Thanks for the following individuals for leaving some amazing reviews: chimmychambo, Ekann000, JFritzsky, Lynch583114, Shwin3, stevey-rudd, Tommy Lawler, and Wrenchell. How to Listen
